title: Grateful Dead Live at Cape Cod Coliseum on 1979-10-27
lineage: Master Cassettes (Nakamichi DR-1)> Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.6 MHz) > dBpoweramp 24/96 > Adobe Audition CC 2019 > TLH flac2496eg: DAT > SoundBlast Audigy X2 > SHN
description:
Set I
Jack Straw
Candyman
Me & My Uncle >
Big River
Brown Eyed Women
Easy To Love You
New Minglewood Blues
Stagger Lee
Lost Sailor >
Saint Of Circumstance >
Deal
Set II
Dancing In The Street >

The Other One >
Drums >
Not Fade Away >
Black Peter >
Around & Around

Encore:
One More Saturday Night


Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
